                            <comment id="15318714" author="blambov" created="Tue, 7 Jun 2016 15:45:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank for the patch. I would not change the array size to still catch the bug of compressor using the size of the array instead of passed length. Fixing just the &lt;tt&gt;arrayCopy&lt;/tt&gt; should be enough to sort the problem.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15321348" author="reiodaira" created="Wed, 8 Jun 2016 20:05:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, I agree.  That would be enough.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
